<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Seitz Marschall zu Oberndorf am Lech, Viztum in Oberbayern</head><p>Der Rat teilt wegen der entwendeten Bücher und anderer Sachen des Juden Süßel mit, dass der beschuldigte Kassariel, Jude zu Nürnberg, zu einem Austrag bis Mitfasten bereit ist, wenn Süßel nach Nürnberg kommt.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_218" id="108v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_218_r2l33"><expan>Seitʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> Marſchalk 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan></del> cʒu <expan>Ob<ex>er</ex>ndorff</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l34"><expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vicʒtu<ex>m</ex></expan> Jn Obernbaÿern / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_218_r2l35"><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_218_line_1586685928858_92"><expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab></add> Marſchalk / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / von Süſʒlen des <expan>Jude<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> / vvie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l36">dem <expan>büche<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd ander dingk <expan>entrage<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeÿ vvoꝛden / vnd das er beÿ kaſſariel </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l37">dem augenartʒt beÿ vns mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> verboten hab / vnd begert / daʒ vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l38">mit <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> kaſſariel <expan>Jude<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſchaffe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſullen / daʒ er das <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>endert</expan> laſʒ / biʒ daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l39">Süſʒel Jud <expan>herüb<ex>er</ex></expan> komen müg / Alſo <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen / mit <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l40">kaſſariel geredt / daʒ er ſpricht / Er vvöll das alſo beſteen <expan>laſʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> hiecʒwiſchen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l41">vnd <expan>mitvaſt<ex>en</ex></expan> ſchierſt / daʒ <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> in <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒeit kom / vnd es mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> auſʒtrag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l42">vnd vvo wir etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>purific<ex>acionis</ex></expan> Marie / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_218" id="108v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Seicze<ex>n</ex></expan> Marschalk czu
                            <expan>Ob<ex>er</ex>ndorff</expan>, <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <expan>vicztu<ex>m</ex></expan> in
                        Obernbayern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan></add> Marschalk, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Süszlen, des
                                <expan>jude<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, wie
                        dem <expan>büche<ex>r</ex></expan> und ander dingk
                            <expan>entrage<ex>n</ex></expan> sey worden und das er bey Kassariel,
                        dem augenarczt bey uns, mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> verboten hab und begert, daz wir mit
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan> Kassariel,
                            <expan>jude<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>schaffe<ex>n</ex></expan> sullen,
                        daz er das <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>endert</expan> lasz, biz daz Süszel, jud,
                                <expan>herüb<ex>er</ex></expan> komen müg; also
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        willen mit <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan> Kassariel geredt, daz er
                        spricht, er wöll das also besteen <expan>lasze<ex>n</ex></expan>
                            hieczwischen und <app><note><q type="date"><expan>mitvast<ex>en</ex></expan> schierst</q>22.03.1411</note></app>, daz
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> in <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> zeit kom und es
                        mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> ausztrag. Und wo wir etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>purific<ex>acionis</ex></expan> Marie. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
